    {
      "id": "CHAPITA_INFO",
      "title": "Chapita QR",
      "data": {},
      "layout": {
        "type": "SingleColumnLayout",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "TextHeading",
            "text": "ℹ️ Chapita QR"
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBody",
            "text": "La chapita QR de Sigo Tu Huella es una identificación digital para tu mascota.\n\n🔹 Cómo funciona:\n1. Pedís la chapita\n2. La adherís al collar\n3. Si alguien la encuentra, escanea el QR y ve tus datos de contacto\n\n🔹 Ventajas:\n• Sin números grabados (seguro)\n• Podés actualizar tus datos\n• Sin cuotas ni renovaciones"
          },
          {
            "type": "Footer",
            "label": "Solicitar chapita",
            "on-click-action": {
              "name": "navigate",
              "next": {
                "type": "screen",
                "name": "CHAPITA_FORM"
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAPITA_FORM",
      "title": "Solicitar chapita",
      "data": {
        "pet_name": { "type": "string", "__example__": "Luna" },
        "species": { "type": "string", "__example__": "dog" },
        "requester_name": { "type": "string", "__example__": "Juan" }
      },
      "layout": {
        "type": "SingleColumnLayout",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "TextHeading",
            "text": "Solicitar chapita QR"
          },
          {
            "type": "TextInput",
            "name": "pet_name",
            "label": "Nombre de tu mascota"
          },
          {
            "type": "RadioButtonsGroup",
            "name": "species",
            "label": "Especie",
            "data-source": [
              { "id": "dog", "title": "🐕 Perro" },
              { "id": "cat", "title": "🐱 Gato" },
              { "id": "other", "title": "🐾 Otro" }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "TextInput",
            "name": "requester_name",
            "label": "Tu nombre"
          },
          {
            "type": "Footer",
            "label": "Enviar solicitud",
            "on-click-action": {
              "name": "complete",
              "payload": {}
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "DONATE_INFO",
      "title": "Donar",
      "data": {
        "donation_method": { "type": "string", "__example__": "transfer" }
      },
      "layout": {
        "type": "SingleColumnLayout",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "TextHeading",
            "text": "💰 Donar"
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBody",
            "text": "¡Gracias por querer ayudar! 🙌\n\nCada donación se destina a:\n🐾 Atención veterinaria\n🍖 Alimento para rescatados\n🏠 Refugio transitorio\n\n¿Cómo querés donar?"
          },
          {
            "type": "RadioButtonsGroup",
            "name": "donation_method",
            "label": "Método de donación",
            "data-source": [
              { "id": "transfer", "title": "🏦 Transferencia bancaria" },
              { "id": "mercadopago", "title": "💳 Mercado Pago" },
              { "id": "share", "title": "📲 Compartir para difundir" }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "Footer",
            "label": "Continuar",
            "on-click-action": {
              "name": "data_exchange",
              "payload": {}
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "DONATE_SHOW",
      "title": "Donar",
      "data": {
        "accounts_text": { "type": "string", "__example__": "Alias: sigotuhuella.mp\nCBU: 00000000000000" },
        "mp_link": { "type": "string", "__example__": "https://mpago.la/xxxxx" }
      },
      "layout": {
        "type": "SingleColumnLayout",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "TextHeading",
            "text": "💰 Donar"
          },
          {
            "type": "TextBody",
            "text": "$.accounts_text"
          },
          {
            "type": "Footer",
            "label": "Ya doné",
            "on-click-action": {
              "name": "complete",
              "payload": {}
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
